<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-03-26T08:54:15-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-03-26T08:54:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-26T08:54:15-04:00</updated><title>迪士尼+有一个新的Hulu化标志</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lowT95d_t7nI7VnisReNjBi1wCE=/0x10:1920x1290/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73233411 /Disney_logo_update_hed.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;旧的 Disney Plus 图标徽标（左）与更新后的青色徽标（右）相比。&lt;/em>; |图片：迪士尼&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;aoXoiA&quot;>;迪士尼对其迪士尼+流媒体服务的徽标和启动屏幕进行了一些细微但值得注意的更新，这可能是对其&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2023/12/6/23990787/disney-plus-hulu-one-app-experience-beta-launch&quot;>;即将与 Hulu 合并&lt;/a>;。最大的变化是新的青色/海泡沫背景颜色，它似乎是原始蓝色背景和 Hulu 使用的绿色的粗略混合。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tDd3qn&quot;>;仅从表面上看，更新后的颜色设计——已经可以在迪士尼+网站和各种应用商店上看到——对这家企业巨头来说很有意义。除了与 Hulu 明显的统一之外，新的颜色还使其在 Prime Video、Max 和 Paramount Plus 等其他流媒体服务使用的蓝色和黑色徽标的海洋中更加突出。但看到旧徽标消失，我实际上感到很难过。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;我... &lt;/cite>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112300/disney-plus-new-logo-hulu-green-青色&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112300/disney-plus-new-logo-hulu-green-teal" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112300/disney-plus-new-logo-hulu-green-teal</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-26T08:34:11-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-26T08:34:11-04:00</updated><title> PS5 正在获得自动游戏剪辑功能，以帮助其他玩家</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;索尼 PS5 主机。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wlDvmAWRYQni4gwtXrnMwhudER4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73233403/vpavic_4278_20201030_0292.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Vjeran Pavic / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;xGXbj9&quot;>;索尼将于今年晚些时候在 PS5 上推出新的社区游戏帮助功能，该功能旨在自动创建剪辑，帮助其他玩家。 PS5 玩家将能够自动上传游戏玩法，以帮助制作游戏开发者提供的提示视频。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;mYlp6q&quot;>;选择加入体验将使您的 PS5 在您完成任务时自动捕获游戏剪辑。支持的标题中的活动。 “然后，它将由主持人审核，如果获得批准，您的视频将作为游戏帮助提示发布，供 PlayStation 玩家观看、学习和评分。” &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.playstation .com/2024/03/26/introducing-community-game-help-a-new-enhancement-for-game-help-powered-by-user- generated-content/?sf272392794=1&quot;>;解释 Sabrina Meditz&lt;/ a>;，PS5 平台体验产品管理高级总监。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：索尼&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;PS5 玩家将收到通知如果他们...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112309/sony-ps5-community-game -help&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112309/sony-ps5-community-game-help" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112309/sony-ps5-community-game-help</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-26T08:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-26T08:00:00-04:00</updated><title>这就是为什么人工智能搜索引擎真的无法杀死谷歌</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;聊天机器人摆动到 Google 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HJXKqKbqTjDSaZz3Drs_d3gNqhE=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73233337/IMG_4450.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;文森特·基尔布赖德 (Vincent Kilbride) 插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;人工智能搜索工具正在变得越来越好，但他们还不了解搜索引擎到底是什么以及我们如何真正使用它们。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24111326/ai-search-perplexity-copilot-you-google-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24111326/ai-search-perplexity-copilot-you-google-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24111326/ai-search-perplexity-copilot-you-google-review</id><author><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-26T06:34:33-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-26T06:34:33-04:00</updated><title> Canva 收购 Affinity 以填补其设计套件中 Adob​​e 大小的漏洞</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;白色背景上的 Canva 和 Affinity 徽标。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Zd0tMJQkHsAFlfnzMa-Lc8Si7dM=/0x94:2568x1806/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73233235/Canva_affinity_banner_2.31c4b05d.5。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Affinity 的专业设计软件可以为 Canva 提供与 Adob​​e 激烈竞争所需的优势。&lt;/em>; |图片：Canva&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;99Fs0f&quot;>;基于网络的设计平台 Canva 已收购&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp ;url=https%3A%2F%2Faffinity.serif.com%2Fen-us%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F3%2F26%2F24112277%2Fcanva -affinity-acquisition-design-software-suite-adobe-rival&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Affinity 创意软件套件&lt;/a>;，将自己定位为 Adob​​e 对数字设计行业控制的挑战者。 Canva &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canva.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fnews%2Faffinity%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge。 com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F3%2F26%2F24112277%2Fcanva-affinity-acquisition-design-software-suite-adobe-rival&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot; _blank&quot;>;周二宣布了该交易&lt;/a>;，该交易赋予该公司对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/11/9/23448945/affinity-version-2-adobe- Creative-app-features-price&quot;>;Affinity Designer、Photo 和 Publisher&lt;/a>; — 适用于 Windows、Mac 和 iPad 的三种流行创意应用程序，分别提供与 Adob​​e Illustrator、Photoshop 和 InDesign 软件类似的功能。&lt;/a>; p>; &lt;p id=&quot;AnIW9E&quot;>;该交易的官方数据尚未公布，但&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/canva-acquires- affinity-design-suite-in-push-to-rival-adobe?embedded-checkout=true&quot;>;&lt;em>;彭博社&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;报道称其价值“数亿[英国]英镑”。尽管如此，随着这家总部位于澳大利亚的公司试图吸引更多创意专业人士，此次收购还是有意义的。截至 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canva.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fnews%2Fcanva-us-growth%2F&amp;amp ;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F3%2F26%2F24112277%2Fcanva-affinity-acquisition-design-software-suite-adobe-rival&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;今年一月&lt;/a>;，Canva 的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112277/ canva-affinity-acquisition-design-software-suite-adobe-rival&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112277/canva-affinity-acquisition-design-software-suite-adobe-rival" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/26/24112277/canva-affinity-acquisition-design-software-suite-adobe-rival</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-25T21:53:10-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-25T21:53:10-04:00</updated><title>以下是目前最优惠的 Apple Watch 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在 Apple Watch SE (2022) 上为 Stripes 表盘建模时拿着钱包的女士&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/N67pZRCs03NPTb3sEufuexCY-8A=/0x0: 2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/66976955/226292_Apple_Watch_SE_PHO_akrales_0047.38.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;如果有的话，入门级 Apple Watch SE 就是一款网关智能手表.&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;nHQiE2&quot;>;9 月份，苹果推出了最新一批智能手表，推出了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/23878981/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-review-double-tap- precision-finding-siri&quot;>;Apple Watch Ultra 2&lt;/a>;（799 美元）以及新款 &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/23878981/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-review-double-tap- precision-finding-siri&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 9&lt;/a>;（399 美元）。每款可穿戴设备都有自己的优点和缺点，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23369207/apple-watch-se-2022-review-smartwatch&quot;>;第二代 Apple Watch SE&lt;/ a>;（249 美元），但新款可穿戴设备的推出也意味着现在市场上的 Apple Watch 型号比以往任何时候都多，而且还有更多优惠。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float -left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;CWUc7k&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何选择购买哪款 Apple Watch&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23037217/apple-watch-series-9-ultra-2-second-gen-se-best-smartwatch-how- to&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;目前最优惠的 AirPods&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals&quot;},{&quot;title&quot; :&quot;watchOS 10 预览版：小部件一路向下&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23786155/watchos-10-preview-apple-watch&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt; /aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;sHcaqK&quot;>;但是有了所有这些选项，您应该选择哪一个？一般来说，您希望购买您能买得起的最新款手表，以便它能够继续接收来自 Apple 的软件更新。最新的更新 watchOS 10 于 9 月份在 Apple Watch Series 4 及更新机型上推出，尽管没有人能确定 Series 4 是否会获得该更新...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21289209/best-apple-watch-deals</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name><name>卡梅伦·福克纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-25T21:07:49-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-25T21:07:49-04:00</updated><title>日产宣布计划到 2026 年生产 16 款新电动汽车</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Nissan 的 Ariya 电动 SUV，金色油漆&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0-iSc4rrvgWBujk0sIWOlhu-_-0=/258x0:5231x3315/1310x873/cdn. vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73232771/2023_Nissan_Ariya_US_44.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：日产&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;kQVTOj&quot;>;日产有 &lt;a href= “https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20240325809457/en/Nissan-Launches-The-Arc-Business-Plan-to-Drive-Value-and-Enhance-Competitiveness-and-Profitability/?feedref= JJAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-Q-tiwWZwkcswR1UZtV7eGe24xL9TZOyQUMS3J72mJlQ7fxFuNFTHSunhvli30RlBNXya2izy9YOgHlBiZQk2LOzmn6JePCpHPCiYGaEx4DL1Rq8pNwkf3AarimpDzQGuQ%3D%3D &quot;>;制定了一项新计划&lt;/a>;，到 2026 年其生产的 30 辆汽车中，有 16 辆将实现电动化，其余则改用内燃机。对于我们这些北美人来说，该公司表示计划在美国和加拿大发布七款新车，尽管尚不清楚其中有多少是某种类型的电动汽车。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5KdWb6&quot; >;日产表示，美国正在推出“e-POWER 和插电式混合动力车型”——每种车型都使用电力和燃料的混合动力。目前，日产唯一生产的全电动电动汽车是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/12/24035857/nissans-ariya-gets-the-nismo-treatment&quot; >;Ariya SUV&lt;/a>; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/7/14/23219044/nissan-leaf-phase-out-discontinue-ev-pioneer&quot;>;可能濒临灭绝&lt; /a>; （或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24092258/the-2024-nissan-leaf-gets-the-us-ev-tax-credit&quot;>;也许不是&lt;/a>;）叶子。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;BWeZzr&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data- anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;拜登采用汽车制造商和工会首选的新汽车排放规则&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 3/20/24106638/biden-epa-vehicle-emissions-final-standards-electric-hybrid&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;电动汽车过渡通过自己的电线绊倒&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www .theverge.com/23934889/electric-vehicle-ev-transition-sales-delays-politics&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;SgxSPn&quot;>;2021 年，日产表示将&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/11/29/22807700/nissan-electric-vehicle-investment-plan-concepts&quot;>;到2030年生产23辆电动汽车&lt;/a>;，其中 15 辆将是纯电动汽车，而不是某种形式的混合动力汽车。很难说是否...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111963/nissan-ev-plan-2026-solid-state-电池&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111963/nissan-ev-plan-2026-solid-state-batteries" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111963/nissan-ev-plan-2026-solid-state-batteries</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-25T19:51:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-25T19:51:30-04:00</updated><title>微软任命了新的 Windows 和 Surface 负责人</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;微软徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/s7hTrdZLaxmCEfADTQuYdmThLG4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73232686/STK095_Microsoft_04.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;gRsFtf&quot;>;微软今天任命 Pavan Davuluri 为其新的 Windows 和 Surface 主管。去年 Panos Panay&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/27/23892462/amazon-hires-panos-panay-microsoft&quot;>;意外离开&lt;/a>;前往亚马逊后，微软 &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/18/23878759/microsoft-windows-panos-panay-surface-yusuf-mehdi&quot;>;将 Windows 和 Surface 组拆分为两个组&lt;/a>;不同的领导者。 Davuluri 接管了 Surface 芯片和设备工作，Mikhail Parakhin 领导了一个专注于 Windows 和网络体验的新团队。现在，Windows 和 Surface 都将由 Davuluri 负责，因为 Parakhin 已“决定探索新角色”。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;zTcadi&quot;>;&lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>; 已获得 Rajesh Jha 的内部备忘录微软体验和设备主管概述了新的 Windows 组织。微软现在再次整合其 Windows 和设备团队。 “这将使我们能够采取整体方法来构建......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111931/microsoft-windows-surface -pavan-davuluri&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111931/microsoft-windows-surface-pavan-davuluri" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111931/microsoft-windows-surface-pavan-davuluri</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-25T19:29:18-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-25